---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Protocol | Singular">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">The Singular Protocol</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">A Decentralized Investment Engine</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Step 1: Capital Allocation -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-800 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-blue-500">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">1</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Capital Allocation</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            The DAO deploys capital from its treasury into promising new ventures. This is done via a formal, community-led process where Singular Investment Proposals (SIPs) are submitted, debated, and voted on by SNG holders.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Portfolio Growth -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-800 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-green-500">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">2</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Portfolio Growth</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            As the protocol's investments mature and succeed, the treasury's Net Asset Value (NAV) increases. Because the supply of SNG is fixed, the SNG token, which represents a direct claim on these assets, appreciates in value accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Value Realization -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-800 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-purple-500">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">3</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Value Realization</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Through a governance vote, the DAO can decide to sell a portion of a successful investment to realize profits. This converts on-paper gains into tangible assets like stablecoins, which are returned to the DAO treasury.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Return to Holders -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-800 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-yellow-500">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">4</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Return to Holders (Dividends)</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            A portion of the realized profits can be returned directly to SNG token holders as a dividend. This completes the value cycle and rewards long-term commitment and effective governance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
